            </div>
        </form>
    


<%# HELPERS TO WRITE %>

    <div class="row align-items-md-stretch p-5">
        <div class="col-md-6 px-5 mb-3">
            <div class="p-3 bg-body-tertiary border rounded-3">
            <h5>If you do not have any ideas:</h5><hr>
            <p>Choose the first event which comes to mind</p>
            <p>Proper form does not matter</p>
            <p>Consider it fiction</p> 
            <p>Allow reactions, emotional responses, feelings</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    
        <div class="col-md-6 px-5 mb-3">
            <div class="p-3 bg-body-tertiary border rounded-3">
            <h5>This may help also:</h5><hr>
            <p>Name three things you're grateful for</p>
            <p>Three amazing things that happened today</p>
            <p>What would make today great?</p>
            <p>How could You have made today even better?</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

